WEBVTT

00:01.302 --> 00:08.273
♪♪

00:08.275 --> 00:11.877
McLeod: IN 2015 --
AUGUST 4 OF 2015 --

00:11.879 --> 00:17.099
I RECEIVED THE NEWS THAT I HAVE
TERMINAL BREAST CANCER,

00:17.101 --> 00:20.219
AND THEY GAVE ME
SIX MONTHS TO TWO YEARS.

00:23.190 --> 00:25.607
[ Voice breaking ]
BUT MY DOCTORS NEVER ASKED ME

00:25.609 --> 00:27.309
IF I WANTED TO LIVE.

00:27.311 --> 00:29.094
THEY JUST ASSUME EVERYBODY DOES.

00:29.096 --> 00:31.647
♪♪

00:31.649 --> 00:37.069
AFTER THE SHOCK WORE OFF,
I WAS ACTUALLY KIND OF EXCITED.

00:37.071 --> 00:39.204
WHENEVER IT'S MY TIME,
IT'S MY TIME.

00:39.206 --> 00:41.373
I'M COMFORTABLE WITH THAT.

00:41.375 --> 00:44.827
BUT HERE I AM, I-I'M STILL HERE,

00:44.829 --> 00:47.996
SO I OBVIOUSLY SERVE
SOME PURPOSE.

00:47.998 --> 00:54.920
♪♪

01:04.932 --> 01:10.069
I WAS KIND OF UNSURE ABOUT
TALKING ABOUT IT AGAIN.

01:10.071 --> 01:12.938
BUT IF IT HELPS ANOTHER PERSON

01:12.940 --> 01:15.908
NOT GET TRAPPED
IN A SITUATION LIKE MINE,

01:15.910 --> 01:19.178
THEN IT'S FOR THE RIGHT REASONS.

01:19.180 --> 01:24.116
SINGLE WOMEN WHO HAVE CHILDREN
NEED TO BE VERY CAUTIOUS.

01:26.087 --> 01:29.655
THERE ARE TOO MANY THINGS
I SHOULD HAVE SEEN.

01:29.657 --> 01:32.291
IF SOMETHING FEELS WRONG
IN YOUR GUT,

01:32.293 --> 01:34.460
YOU HAVE TO LISTEN TO IT.

01:35.930 --> 01:39.798
BUT I DIDN'T. I DIDN'T KNOW
SCOTT KIMBALL IS EVIL.

01:39.800 --> 01:43.852
♪♪

01:43.854 --> 01:46.838
I'M VERY CERTAIN
HE HAD A PLAN ALL ALONG.

01:46.840 --> 01:50.342
♪♪

01:50.344 --> 01:52.895
[ THE PAPER CHASE'S "WHAT'S SO
AMAZING ABOUT GRACE?" PLAYS ]

01:52.897 --> 01:55.948
[ STRINGS CONTINUE
PLAYING SINISTER TUNE ]

01:55.950 --> 02:01.003
[ STATIC CRACKLING ]

02:01.005 --> 02:02.771
[ KNOCK AT DOOR ]
[ CREAKING ]

02:02.773 --> 02:08.093
[ BANGING ON DOOR ]

02:08.095 --> 02:13.198
[ CREAKING ]

02:13.200 --> 02:15.751
[ WATER DRIPPING ]

02:15.753 --> 02:18.353
[ BANGING ON DOOR ]
[ CREAKING ]

02:18.355 --> 02:19.688
[ SINISTER CHORD STRIKES ]

02:19.690 --> 02:22.641
-- Captions by VITAC --
 www.vitac.com

02:22.643 --> 02:25.527
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

02:25.529 --> 02:27.813
♪♪

02:27.815 --> 02:33.285
KAYSI'S FATHER AND I DIVORCED
WHEN SHE WAS VERY YOUNG,

02:33.287 --> 02:36.205
AND HAD NOT REALLY
DATED MUCH AT ALL

02:36.207 --> 02:37.873
AFTER MY SECOND DIVORCE.

02:37.875 --> 02:42.494
♪♪

02:42.496 --> 02:47.299
I MET SCOTT KIMBALL AT A CASINO
IN BLACK HAWK, COLORADO.

02:49.170 --> 02:53.205
HIS MOTHER WAS WHEELCHAIR-BOUND.

02:53.207 --> 02:54.773
HE MOVED AROUND
THE FURNITURE FOR HER

02:54.775 --> 02:56.808
SO SHE COULD
SIT WITH US AND PLAY.

02:56.810 --> 02:59.811
AND I THINK ALL WOMEN
LOOK AT MEN

02:59.813 --> 03:01.713
WHO ARE KIND TO THEIR MOTHER

03:01.715 --> 03:05.717
AND THEY THINK THAT THEY
MIGHT MAKE A GOOD PARTNER.

03:05.719 --> 03:07.436
SO WE CHATTED FOR A WHILE.

03:07.438 --> 03:10.405
-I'M SCOTT.
-LORI.

03:10.407 --> 03:11.556
-HI.
-HI.

03:11.558 --> 03:13.075
HE HAD A VERY NICE SMILE.

03:13.077 --> 03:15.360
YOU BETTER WATCH OUT FOR HER.
SHE'S A SHARK.

03:15.362 --> 03:17.696
[ LAUGHS ]
HE SEEMED PRETTY AMAZING.

03:17.698 --> 03:20.899
HE TOLD ME THAT HE HAD
TWO YOUNG SONS.

03:20.901 --> 03:22.417
HE ONLY HAD THEM PART-TIME.

03:22.419 --> 03:25.070
AND I REALLY THOUGHT
I WOULD NEVER DATE SOMEBODY

03:25.072 --> 03:26.905
THAT HAD SMALL CHILDREN,

03:26.907 --> 03:29.374
BUT HE WAS SO APPEALING.

03:29.376 --> 03:32.094
SO I WROTE MY NUMBER DOWN
ON A PIECE OF PAPER

03:32.096 --> 03:34.913
AND I SLID MY NUMBER TO HIM.

03:34.915 --> 03:38.800
AND I KEPT MY FINGERS ON TOP
OF THE PIECE OF PAPER

03:38.802 --> 03:41.136
AND I SAID, "YOU'RE NOT A FELON
OR ANYTHING, ARE YOU?"

03:41.138 --> 03:42.271
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:42.273 --> 03:45.023
McLeod: HE TOLD ME
HE WORKED FOR THE FBI,

03:45.025 --> 03:48.093
AND HE COULDN'T BE A FELON
AND WORK FOR THE FBI.

03:48.095 --> 03:50.395
AND THEN I THOUGHT,

03:50.397 --> 03:54.650
IF THE FBI TRUSTS HIM,
WHY WOULD I NOT TRUST HIM?

03:54.652 --> 03:56.735
WELL, I ACTUALLY HAVE
TO HEAD OUT.

03:56.737 --> 03:59.571
BUT YOU'VE GOT MY NUMBER.

03:59.573 --> 04:01.940
OKAY, BYE.
-GOOD NIGHT.

04:01.942 --> 04:11.950
♪♪

04:11.952 --> 04:21.459
♪♪

04:21.461 --> 04:23.395
♪♪

04:23.397 --> 04:26.431
McLeod:
WE GOT RELATIVELY CLOSE FAST.

04:26.433 --> 04:30.235
ALLOWING SOMEBODY ELSE TO
TAKE ME OUT AND PAY FOR MEALS

04:30.237 --> 04:32.654
AND THINGS LIKE THAT,
IT FELT GOOD.

04:32.656 --> 04:36.358
BUT WHEN WE STARTED
STAYING TOGETHER AT MY HOUSE,

04:36.360 --> 04:39.911
HE WOULD TAKE OFF IN
THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

04:39.913 --> 04:41.613
WHAT'S GOING ON?

04:41.615 --> 04:44.149
IT WAS ALWAYS
BECAUSE HE HAD TO WORK.

04:44.151 --> 04:47.786
AND IF HE LEAVES
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT,

04:47.788 --> 04:50.339
I-I'M NOT ALLOWED TO KNOW
WHERE HE'S GOING.

04:50.341 --> 04:53.125
SORRY, LORI,
I TOLD YOU ABOUT THIS.

04:53.127 --> 04:55.377
IT'S MY JOB.

04:55.379 --> 04:58.964
YOU MENTIONED YOU HAD
TO WORK LATE SOMETIMES.

04:58.966 --> 05:00.432
BUT WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

05:01.435 --> 05:03.518
HE TOLD ME HE WORKS UNDERCOVER.

05:03.520 --> 05:07.005
HE CAN'T TELL ME ANYTHING.
IT'S FOR MY OWN SAFETY.

05:07.007 --> 05:09.775
HE WAS LIKE NAILING JELL-O
TO A WALL.

05:09.777 --> 05:14.512
I CAN'T SAY,
BUT IT IS IMPORTANT.

05:14.514 --> 05:16.198
JUST EXPLAIN IT TO ME.

05:16.200 --> 05:19.451
HE BROKE HIS OWN RULE
AND HE TOLD ME

05:19.453 --> 05:22.037
ABOUT A CASE THAT
HE WAS WORKING ON.

05:22.039 --> 05:23.238
ALL RIGHT.

05:26.493 --> 05:30.295
I AM WORKING ON A CASE
OF A WOMAN NAMED JENNIFER

05:30.297 --> 05:32.964
THAT I BELIEVE WAS MURDERED.

05:32.966 --> 05:37.419
A GIRL NAMED JENNIFER HAD
BEEN KILLED BY DRUG DEALERS.

05:37.421 --> 05:40.722
THAT WAS ALL THE INFORMATION
HE LET ME HAVE.

05:40.724 --> 05:42.341
SO I KNOW IT'S HARD,
BUT IT'S BEST

05:42.343 --> 05:45.010
IF I DON'T TELL YOU
WHERE I'M GOING.

05:45.012 --> 05:48.563
IT'S SAFER FOR US. OKAY?

05:48.565 --> 05:49.731
OKAY, YEAH.

05:52.269 --> 05:56.721
IT BOTHERED ME THAT
I DIDN'T KNOW EVERYTHING,

05:56.723 --> 05:59.274
BUT HE ASSURED ME
IT WAS FOR MY OWN SAFETY,

05:59.276 --> 06:00.992
AND I DROPPED IT.

06:00.994 --> 06:03.362
I-I NEVER DISCUSSED IT
WITH HIM AGAIN.

06:03.364 --> 06:09.918
♪♪

06:09.920 --> 06:11.086
-Scott: COME ON IN.
-ALL RIGHT.

06:12.539 --> 06:14.673
McLeod: THE FIRST TIME
I WENT TO HIS HOUSE,

06:14.675 --> 06:17.843
I COULD TELL IT HAD BEEN
DECORATED BY A WOMAN.

06:19.596 --> 06:22.747
-THIS IS THE PLACE.
-YEAH.

06:22.749 --> 06:26.685
THERE WERE ANGELS,
LOTS OF ANGEL PICTURES,

06:26.687 --> 06:28.470
ANGELS ON THE HEARTH...

06:28.472 --> 06:30.889
LET ME GO GET
A BOTTLE OF WINE.

06:30.891 --> 06:32.023
ALL RIGHT.

06:33.861 --> 06:35.427
...CERTAINLY NOT FURNITURE

06:35.429 --> 06:38.029
THAT A MAN WITH TWO CHILDREN
WOULD BUY.

06:40.234 --> 06:41.650
I SAID,
"ARE YOU DATING SOMEBODY?

06:41.652 --> 06:43.952
"SHOULD I BE AFRAID
OF ANOTHER WOMAN?

06:43.954 --> 06:45.537
SHOULD I EVEN BE HERE?"

06:45.539 --> 06:46.822
DID YOU DECORATE THIS,

06:46.824 --> 06:49.541
OR DO YOU HAVE A WIFE YOU'RE
NOT TELLING ME ABOUT?

06:49.543 --> 06:51.776
[ LAUGHS ] I HAVEN'T
BEEN HERE VERY LONG.

06:51.778 --> 06:53.161
IT'S MY FRIEND JENNIFER'S
PLACE.

06:53.163 --> 06:56.298
I'M JUST LEASING IT
FROM HER SINCE SHE MOVED.

06:56.300 --> 06:59.918
I SAID, "IS IT THE SAME GIRL
THAT YOU THINK IS DEAD?"

07:00.971 --> 07:04.289
OH! NO, NO, JUST
THE SAME FIRST NAME.

07:04.291 --> 07:05.474
I'M SORRY.

07:05.476 --> 07:08.510
HE SAID, "SEE, I HAVE
A LEASE THAT WE WROTE UP.

07:08.512 --> 07:10.562
I AM LEASING HER FURNITURE."

07:10.564 --> 07:14.132
I HAVE A COPY OF THE LEASE
AGREEMENT RIGHT HERE.

07:14.134 --> 07:17.903
IT DID SEEM ODD THAT HE WOULD
OFFER AN EXPLANATION

07:17.905 --> 07:20.188
PRETTY MUCH BEFORE
I EVEN ASKED THE QUESTION.

07:20.190 --> 07:22.441
BUT THERE WERE
NO OTHER SIGNS OF A WOMAN.

07:22.443 --> 07:28.113
THERE WERE NOT
BATHROOM PRODUCTS, MAKEUP.

07:28.115 --> 07:30.532
THERE WAS NOTHING LIKE THAT
THAT WOULD LEAD ME TO BELIEVE

07:30.534 --> 07:33.869
THAT ANOTHER WOMAN WAS
LIVING THERE.

07:33.871 --> 07:37.589
COME ON, LET ME SHOW YOU
THE REST OF THE PLACE.

07:37.591 --> 07:39.374
WE DROPPED THE TOPIC.

07:39.376 --> 07:42.544
I JUST LEARNED NOT TO QUESTION.

07:42.546 --> 07:49.834
♪♪

07:49.836 --> 07:52.854
SCOTT TOLD ME THAT
HE FOUND A FARMHOUSE

07:52.856 --> 07:54.723
FOR ALL OF US TO LIVE IN.

07:54.725 --> 07:56.791
MY DAUGHTER KAYSI MET HIS SONS,

07:56.793 --> 07:58.844
AND THEY ALL SEEMED
TO GET ALONG VERY WELL.

07:58.846 --> 08:02.013
IT WAS JUST THE PERFECT
ENVIRONMENT FOR EVERYBODY.

08:02.015 --> 08:03.031
WELL, I'M JUST ABOUT TO HEAD

08:03.033 --> 08:06.284
TO THE GROCERY STORE
HERE IN A SECOND.

08:06.286 --> 08:08.870
BUT ONE DAY, SCOTT HAD GONE
ON A BUSINESS TRIP

08:08.872 --> 08:10.355
AND HE CALLED ME AND ASKED ME

08:10.357 --> 08:13.291
TO USE HIS VEHICLE
WHILE HE WAS GONE.

08:13.293 --> 08:14.526
WHY?

08:14.528 --> 08:16.294
MINE WAS ACTUALLY NICER.

08:16.296 --> 08:20.465
BUT HE SAID JUST DRIVE IT
DAY IN, DAY OUT, WHATEVER,

08:20.467 --> 08:21.750
WHILE HE WAS AWAY.

08:21.752 --> 08:24.135
I DON'T KNOW WHY
HE ASKED ME TO DO IT,

08:24.137 --> 08:26.505
BUT IT WASN'T WORTH
TALKING ABOUT IT.

08:26.507 --> 08:28.173
HE JUST WANTED ME TO DO IT.

08:28.175 --> 08:29.207
I DID IT.

08:29.209 --> 08:30.642
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
THE BIG DEAL IS,

08:30.644 --> 08:32.894
BUT IF IT'S THAT
IMPORTANT TO YOU, SURE.

08:32.896 --> 08:34.546
AND THEN HE SAID,

08:34.548 --> 08:36.815
"OH, BY THE WAY,
I FORGOT TO TELL YOU.

08:36.817 --> 08:38.517
"I FORGOT TO MAKE A DEPOSIT.

08:38.519 --> 08:40.552
"THERE'S A $5,000 CHECK.

08:40.554 --> 08:42.687
"CAN YOU PLEASE JUST
DROP THAT AT MY BANK?

08:42.689 --> 08:44.673
I COMPLETELY FORGOT."

08:44.675 --> 08:49.327
OKAY, SURE, I CAN TAKE IT
ON THE WAY TO GET GROCERIES.

08:49.329 --> 08:50.445
OKAY, LOVE YOU, TOO.

08:50.447 --> 08:52.330
BYE.

08:52.332 --> 08:55.667
TO HAVE $5,000 MISSING
THAT YOU'VE PLUMB FORGOT

08:55.669 --> 08:58.620
TO DEPOSIT SEEMED ODD TO ME.

08:58.622 --> 09:01.840
♪♪

09:01.842 --> 09:05.460
AND WHAT I NOTICED
IN THE MEMO OF THE CHECK

09:05.462 --> 09:09.414
WAS IT SAID, "FOR JENNIFER."

09:09.416 --> 09:12.350
♪♪

09:12.352 --> 09:14.269
IT FELT STRANGE THAT, AGAIN,

09:14.271 --> 09:17.556
WE'VE GOT AN INCIDENT
WITH A JENNIFER.

09:17.558 --> 09:19.558
BUT I DEFINITELY
THOUGHT THAT THE CHECK

09:19.560 --> 09:23.778
WAS SOMETHING HAVING TO DO
WITH AN FBI CASE.

09:25.148 --> 09:26.531
SO I THOUGHT
IT'S JUST ONE MORE THING

09:26.533 --> 09:29.067
I PROBABLY SHOULDN'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT.

09:29.069 --> 09:37.959
♪♪

09:37.961 --> 09:40.378
WE GOT TO THE CAR.

09:40.380 --> 09:41.446
[ SIREN WHOOPS ]

09:41.448 --> 09:44.716
AND WITHIN...
IT FELT LIKE SECONDS,

09:44.718 --> 09:47.469
THERE WERE POLICE CARS ON US.

09:47.471 --> 09:48.920
♪♪

09:50.140 --> 09:55.060
♪♪

09:55.062 --> 09:56.344
OH.

09:56.346 --> 09:59.397
McLeod: ONE NIGHT, WE HAD BEEN
IN BLACK HAWK, GAMBLING.

09:59.399 --> 10:02.067
AND WE GOT TO THE CAR...
[ SIREN WHOOPS ]

10:02.069 --> 10:05.604
AND WITHIN...
IT FELT LIKE SECONDS,

10:05.606 --> 10:08.156
THERE WERE POLICE CARS ON US.

10:08.158 --> 10:09.407
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

10:09.409 --> 10:10.692
-THERE'S NOTHING WRONG.
-YOU'RE UNDER ARREST.

10:10.694 --> 10:11.809
THIS IS JUST PART OF THE JOB.

10:11.811 --> 10:12.911
PUT YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR BACK.

10:12.913 --> 10:15.480
YOU KNOW THIS.
LISTEN, IT'S FINE.

10:15.482 --> 10:18.516
McLeod: AND I WAS JUST IN
STATE OF CONFUSION.

10:18.518 --> 10:20.118
I ASKED SCOTT,
"WHAT'S GOING ON?"

10:20.120 --> 10:23.121
HE SAYS, "LORI, YOU KNOW WHAT
I DO FOR A LIVING.

10:23.123 --> 10:24.923
"THIS IS ALL JUST PART OF IT."

10:24.925 --> 10:28.159
HE WOULD ALWAYS TELL ME
HE WORKS UNDERCOVER,

10:28.161 --> 10:30.011
HE CAN'T TELL ME ANYTHING.

10:30.013 --> 10:32.263
IT'S FOR MY OWN SAFETY.

10:32.265 --> 10:34.349
I DID KNOW THAT
HE HAD SPENT TIME

10:34.351 --> 10:38.670
IN PRISON, UNDERCOVER,
FOR SOME DRUG RING.

10:38.672 --> 10:41.272
[ voice echoes ] CERTAIN THINGS
I CAN'T TELL YOU ABOUT, OKAY?

10:41.274 --> 10:43.475
SO IT WAS ALMOST LIKE A FEELING,

10:43.477 --> 10:45.977
I SHOULD JUST MOVE ALONG,
STOP ASKING QUESTIONS.

10:45.979 --> 10:49.114
YOU KNOW, IT'S NOT THAT BIG
OF A DEAL. JUST MOVE ALONG.

10:49.116 --> 10:50.181
I'LL BE OUT IN NO TIME.

10:50.183 --> 10:53.284
JUST TAKE YOUR CAR
BACK TO THE HOUSE.

10:53.286 --> 10:55.537
AND I'LL LET YOU KNOW
ONCE I GET OUT, OKAY?

10:55.539 --> 10:57.155
OKAY.

10:57.157 --> 10:59.824
McLeod: BUT I REALLY DIDN'T
KNOW WHAT TO THINK.

10:59.826 --> 11:03.328
I WOULDN'T HAVE KNOWN THE RIGHT
QUESTIONS TO ASK HIM ANYWAY.

11:03.330 --> 11:07.132
SO I HAD THREE OR FOUR DAYS
TO WONDER.

11:07.134 --> 11:09.718
AND THE NEXT DAY HE WAS BACK,

11:09.720 --> 11:14.839
SO I HAD NOTHING TO TELL ME
I SHOULD BE CONCERNED.

11:14.841 --> 11:21.813
♪♪

11:21.815 --> 11:23.114
[ GUNSHOT ]

11:23.116 --> 11:26.351
WHEN WE ALL MOVED IN TOGETHER,
I STARTED SEEING HIM

11:26.353 --> 11:29.070
MORPH INTO SOMETHING THAT WAS
A LITTLE MORE HATEFUL.

11:30.273 --> 11:33.641
SCOTT AND I WENT OUT
TO ONE OF THE PASTURES.

11:33.643 --> 11:37.278
HE SAID HE WAS GOING TO TAKE
CARE OF THE PRAIRIE DOGS,

11:37.280 --> 11:42.917
UM, BECAUSE THEY CREATE SUCH
DESTRUCTION IN THE GROUND.

11:42.919 --> 11:46.788
AND SCOTT USED A PELLET GUN
TO KILL THE PRAIRIE DOGS.

11:46.790 --> 11:52.577
AND AS HE WAS FOCUSING ON
ONE PRAIRIE DOG,

11:52.579 --> 11:54.763
HE WOULD SAY, "THIS IS MY MOM,"

11:54.765 --> 11:56.681
AND THEN HE WOULD KILL
THE PRAIRIE DOG.

11:56.683 --> 11:58.416
SO LONG, MOM.
[ GUNSHOT ]

11:58.418 --> 12:01.519
AND THEN HE'D SAY,
"THIS IS MY BROTHER,"

12:01.521 --> 12:03.304
AND THEN HE'D KILL
THAT PRAIRIE DOG.

12:03.306 --> 12:04.522
YOUR TURN, DAD.

12:04.524 --> 12:05.607
[ GUNSHOT ]

12:05.609 --> 12:08.092
AND HE WOULD PICK THEM OFF
ONE BY ONE.

12:08.094 --> 12:10.912
IT WAS NOT A JOKE.
IT WAS NOT FUNNY TO HIM.

12:11.815 --> 12:13.314
[ GUNSHOT ]

12:13.316 --> 12:16.401
AND THAT'S WHEN I SAID, "TELL ME
ONE OF THOSE PRAIRIE DOGS

12:16.403 --> 12:19.204
DOESN'T HAVE MY FACE ON IT."

12:19.206 --> 12:20.538
I WOULDN'T SHOOT YOU.

12:22.325 --> 12:26.828
NO, I'D DO SOMETHING
<i> REALLY</i> SPECIAL FOR YOU.

12:29.549 --> 12:33.418
AND IT SEEMED LIKE IT WAS
MEANT TO BE A THREAT.

12:34.755 --> 12:38.623
IT'S SHOCKING WHEN SOMEBODY
SAYS SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

12:38.625 --> 12:40.175
HE DIDN'T JUST
MAKE IT UP ON THE SPOT.

12:40.177 --> 12:41.976
HE HAD THOUGHT IT THROUGH.

12:41.978 --> 12:43.595
THAT WAS A LITTLE SCARY.

12:43.597 --> 12:45.730
IS HE REALLY THAT CREEPY?

12:45.732 --> 12:48.600
OBVIOUSLY, HE WAS KIDDING
OR I'M LOSING MY MIND.

12:49.736 --> 12:51.186
[ GUNSHOT ]

12:51.188 --> 13:00.645
♪♪

13:00.647 --> 13:03.865
SCOTT APPEARED TO BE
A GREAT FATHER.

13:03.867 --> 13:06.251
PUT THE BOOKS AWAY.
LET'S GO OUTSIDE.

13:06.253 --> 13:07.752
I'LL TEACH YOU
HOW TO BE A MAN.

13:07.754 --> 13:08.920
SCOTT.

13:10.824 --> 13:14.092
BUT HIS OLDEST SON
WAS MORE GENTLE.

13:14.094 --> 13:17.829
HE WAS SOFTER,
AND SCOTT DIDN'T LIKE THAT.

13:17.831 --> 13:20.932
WHAT? HE'S GOTTA LEARN SOMETIME.

13:20.934 --> 13:22.834
COME ON, SUZY.

13:22.836 --> 13:24.936
HE WOULD CALL HIM "SUZY."

13:24.938 --> 13:27.338
AND I JUST --
I THOUGHT IT WAS MEAN.

13:27.340 --> 13:30.024
YOU GUYS GO OUT, AND I'LL HAVE
DINNER READY HERE SOON.

13:32.479 --> 13:37.315
ONE EVENING, THE BOYS WERE OUT
IN THE BACK PASTURE, PLAYING.

13:37.317 --> 13:38.700
EVERYTHING SEEMED FINE.

13:38.702 --> 13:41.019
AND SHORTLY AFTER THAT,
HIS YOUNGEST SON

13:41.021 --> 13:44.739
CAME RUNNING IN THE HOUSE AND HE
SAID, "DAD SAID TO CALL 9-1-1."

13:44.741 --> 13:46.624
HIS BROTHER HAS BEEN HURT.

13:46.626 --> 13:48.660
LORI, CALL AN AMBULANCE!

13:49.863 --> 13:53.364
SCOTT IS RUNNING WITH
HIS SON IN HIS ARMS.

13:53.366 --> 13:56.251
THE STEEL STORM GRATE THAT
WE KEPT OUT AT THE FARM,

13:56.253 --> 13:57.252
IT HAD FALLEN ON HIM.

13:57.254 --> 14:01.706
YES, I NEED AN AMBULANCE
RIGHT AWAY.

14:01.708 --> 14:03.758
SO I CALLED 9-1-1 AND I SAID,

14:03.760 --> 14:06.227
"MY OLDEST STEPSON'S
BEEN INURED.

14:06.229 --> 14:08.680
AND I'M HEARING, 'MY LEG.'"

14:08.682 --> 14:10.265
HIS LEG'S BEEN HURT,
MAYBE BROKEN.

14:10.267 --> 14:11.149
[ BOY GROANS ]

14:11.151 --> 14:13.484
AS I'M TALKING TO THE OPERATOR,

14:13.486 --> 14:16.721
I SEE SCOTT'S VEHICLE TAKE OFF
DOWN THE DIRT DRIVE.

14:16.723 --> 14:18.740
AND I SAID,
"OKAY, I GUESS WE DON'T --

14:18.742 --> 14:22.059
MAYBE IT'S NOT AS BAD
AS I THOUGHT."

14:22.061 --> 14:25.413
HI, YES, HE'S BEING TAKEN
TO THE HOSPITAL RIGHT NOW.

14:25.415 --> 14:26.948
THANK YOU.

14:26.950 --> 14:31.619
AND WE GOT IN THE CAR
AND WE DROVE TO THE HOSPITAL.

14:31.621 --> 14:34.672
OKAY, LET'S GO
AND CATCH UP WITH THEM.

14:34.674 --> 14:41.379
♪♪

14:41.381 --> 14:45.133
I WALKED DOWN THE HALL AND
I LOOKED INTO HIS SON'S ROOM.

14:45.135 --> 14:48.085
♪♪

14:48.087 --> 14:50.605
SCOTT'S COVERED
IN HIS SON'S BLOOD,

14:50.607 --> 14:53.358
AND HIS SON IS
LAYING ON THE TABLE.

14:53.360 --> 14:56.761
AND ALL I WAS THINKING IS,
THIS KID IS NOT VERY BIG.

14:56.763 --> 14:57.762
THAT'S A LOT OF BLOOD.

14:57.764 --> 14:59.597
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

14:59.599 --> 15:04.452
AND THEY SAID THAT HE WAS
INJURED VERY BADLY IN A FALL.

15:04.454 --> 15:06.404
AND I SAID,
"WHAT DID HE FALL OFF OF?

15:06.406 --> 15:09.624
THERE'S NOTHING BACK THERE
HE CAN FALL OFF OF."

15:09.626 --> 15:12.327
THAT'S NOT THE INJURY HE HAD.

15:12.329 --> 15:14.746
IT WASN'T A FALL.
A STORM GRATE FELL ON HIM.

15:14.748 --> 15:17.165
NO, THIS IS FROM AFTER,
WHEN HE FELL OUT OF THE CAR.

15:17.167 --> 15:19.417
OKAY, EXCUSE ME, EXCUSE ME.

15:19.419 --> 15:21.619
SCOTT? WHAT IS THIS?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

15:21.621 --> 15:24.422
HE -- HE JUST FELL OUT
OF THE CAR.

15:26.142 --> 15:30.428
SCOTT TOLD ME THAT
IN THE RIDE TO THE HOSPITAL,

15:30.430 --> 15:32.847
HIS SON REACHED FOR THE WINDOW

15:32.849 --> 15:36.017
TO UNROLL THE WINDOW
TO GET SICK.

15:36.019 --> 15:38.519
AND INSTEAD OF OPENING
THE WINDOW,

15:38.521 --> 15:42.023
HE OPENED THE DOOR
AND HE FELL OUT.

15:43.243 --> 15:47.412
SCOTT SAID HE WAS GOING
ABOUT 60.

15:47.414 --> 15:49.998
AND IT SEEMED SO BIZARRE,

15:50.000 --> 15:53.868
BUT WHAT OTHER EXPLANATION
WOULD THERE BE FOR THAT?

15:53.870 --> 15:58.656
♪♪

15:58.658 --> 16:02.093
AND WITH AS MUCH BLOOD AS I SAW,

16:02.095 --> 16:05.013
I REALLY THOUGHT WE WERE
LOSING HIM THAT NIGHT.

16:06.349 --> 16:10.301
THEY PUT HIM INTO
A CHEMICALLY INDUCED COMA

16:10.303 --> 16:13.805
SO HE WOULD STOP CONVULSING.
HIS BRAIN WAS SWELLING.

16:13.807 --> 16:23.815
♪♪

16:23.817 --> 16:25.283
♪♪

16:25.285 --> 16:30.855
WHEN HE WAS ABLE TO SPEAK,
THE FIRST THING HE SAID WAS,

16:30.857 --> 16:32.824
"WHY DID DAD DO THIS TO ME?"

16:33.877 --> 16:35.192
SCOTT?

16:35.194 --> 16:38.129
♪♪

16:39.416 --> 16:44.769
♪♪

16:44.771 --> 16:46.070
McLeod: WE WERE ALL THERE

16:46.072 --> 16:49.374
WHEN THEY WERE TAKING HIM
OUT OF THE COMA.

16:49.376 --> 16:51.659
AND WHEN THEY STARTED
DRAWING HIM OUT

16:51.661 --> 16:54.362
AND HE WAS ABLE TO SPEAK,

16:54.364 --> 16:57.031
THE FIRST THING HE SAID WAS,

16:57.033 --> 16:59.033
"WHY DID DAD DO THIS TO ME?"

16:59.035 --> 17:00.668
DAD DID IT.

17:00.670 --> 17:05.456
♪♪

17:05.458 --> 17:06.791
HE WAS AFRAID.

17:08.678 --> 17:10.712
I DON'T KNOW
WHY HE PUSHED ME.

17:12.215 --> 17:15.666
AND THE NEUROSURGEON
TURNED AROUND AND HE SAID,

17:15.668 --> 17:16.834
"HE DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S SAYING.

17:16.836 --> 17:18.720
HE HAS A BRAIN INJURY."

17:18.722 --> 17:22.557
IT'S OKAY. HE'S JUST CONFUSED.

17:22.559 --> 17:24.025
SCOTT?

17:24.027 --> 17:26.477
IT'S OKAY, LORI.

17:26.479 --> 17:27.812
I'M JUST GLAD HE'S AWAKE.

17:29.282 --> 17:31.399
I REASONED THROUGH IT.

17:31.401 --> 17:35.019
SCOTT WAS TAKING HIM TO
THE HOSPITAL.

17:35.021 --> 17:36.854
WHY WOULD HE BE TRYING
TO KILL HIM?

17:36.856 --> 17:38.539
IT DIDN'T FIT.

17:38.541 --> 17:41.242
HIS MEMORY WILL
CLEAR UP OVER TIME.

17:41.244 --> 17:42.910
McLeod:
WHEN THE NEUROSURGEON SAID,

17:42.912 --> 17:44.796
"HE DOESN'T KNOW WHAT
HE'S SAYING,"

17:44.798 --> 17:49.550
IT JUST KIND OF CEMENTED
WHAT I ALREADY FELT.

17:49.552 --> 17:52.503
I FELT HE HAD A BAD MEMORY.

17:52.505 --> 17:57.875
♪♪

17:57.877 --> 18:03.047
♪♪

18:03.049 --> 18:05.650
THIS IS SCOTT'S UNCLE TERRY.

18:05.652 --> 18:08.019
SCOTT'S UNCLE TERRY
CAME TO LIVE WITH US

18:08.021 --> 18:10.655
TO TAKE CARE OF WHAT SCOTT
COULDN'T TAKE CARE OF

18:10.657 --> 18:14.859
WHILE SCOTT VISITED HIS SON
EVERYDAY AT THE HOSPITAL.

18:14.861 --> 18:17.161
IT DIDN'T GO VERY SMOOTHLY.

18:17.163 --> 18:21.082
VERY HEAVY DRINKER,
AND HE DIDN'T COVER HIMSELF

18:21.084 --> 18:23.751
WHEN HE WOULD WALK OUT
OF THE BATHROOM.

18:23.753 --> 18:26.921
SCOTT SAID THAT
HE WOULDN'T BE THERE LONG.

18:26.923 --> 18:31.125
AND I CAME HOME
ONE NIGHT FROM WORK

18:31.127 --> 18:32.760
AND I WALKED IN THE HOUSE,

18:32.762 --> 18:35.412
AND ALL OF MY FURNITURE
WAS REARRANGED.

18:35.414 --> 18:38.266
♪♪

18:38.268 --> 18:41.636
I JUST FOUND IT VERY STRANGE.

18:41.638 --> 18:42.804
SCOTT?

18:44.474 --> 18:46.107
I WALKED PAST THE DOOR AND SAW

18:46.109 --> 18:49.310
MY WHITE LEATHER SOFA WAS
OUT BY THE POOL.

18:49.312 --> 18:53.731
AND I COULD SEE
THE HUGE WET SPOT.

18:53.733 --> 18:56.200
SCOTT, WHAT HAPPENED
TO MY COUCH?

18:56.202 --> 18:58.536
IT WAS ONE OF
UNCLE TERRY'S DOGS.

18:59.823 --> 19:02.773
AND SCOTT SAID, "UNCLE TERRY'S
REALLY EMBARRASSED.

19:02.775 --> 19:04.909
"ONE OF THE DOGS GOT SICK
ON YOUR COUCH."

19:04.911 --> 19:07.111
AND I SAID
THAT IS NOT DOG VOMIT.

19:07.113 --> 19:10.214
THAT'S A HUGE STAIN.
THERE'S NO WAY THAT WAS A DOG.

19:10.216 --> 19:13.968
MAYBE IT WAS UNCLE TERRY AND HE
JUST BLAMED IT ON THE DOG.

19:13.970 --> 19:16.220
AND HE SAYS, "WELL MAYBE
HE GOT SICK ON THE COUCH

19:16.222 --> 19:17.972
"AND HE WAS JUST EMBARRASSED.

19:17.974 --> 19:20.057
"BUT IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

19:20.059 --> 19:22.176
HE WON'T BE AROUND ANYMORE."

19:22.178 --> 19:25.813
HE HAD HIT SOME SMALL LOTTERY
AND HE TOOK OFF,

19:25.815 --> 19:29.567
WENT TO MEXICO WITH HIS NEW
GIRLFRIEND, WHO WAS A STRIPPER.

19:31.154 --> 19:34.322
-TERRY?
-THAT'S WHAT HE SAID.

19:34.324 --> 19:37.491
SAID HE'D CALL US
WHEN HE GOT THERE.

19:37.493 --> 19:39.994
I DIDN'T BELIEVE WHAT
HE WAS TELLING ME.

19:39.996 --> 19:42.496
THERE'S NO WAY A WOMAN
WHO'S YOUNG ENOUGH TO STRIP

19:42.498 --> 19:44.365
WOULD BE INTERESTED
IN UNCLE TERRY.

19:44.367 --> 19:46.918
NO WAY.

19:46.920 --> 19:48.336
BUT I REALLY DIDN'T QUESTION IT

19:48.338 --> 19:49.987
BECAUSE I WAS
PERFECTLY COMFORTABLE

19:49.989 --> 19:52.256
WITH HIM BEING OUT OF MY HOUSE.

19:52.258 --> 19:55.760
I WAS HAPPY ABOUT IT
AND I DROPPED IT.

19:55.762 --> 19:57.962
I NEVER DISCUSSED IT
WITH HIM AGAIN.

19:57.964 --> 20:05.386
♪♪

20:05.388 --> 20:08.522
THIS IS THE DAY
KAYSI GRADUATED HIGH SCHOOL.

20:08.524 --> 20:11.392
♪♪

20:11.394 --> 20:15.229
SHE WOUND UP GETTING
INTO HER OWN PLACE

20:15.231 --> 20:19.784
AND TAKING THE ROOMMATE THAT
INTRODUCED HER TO CRYSTAL METH.

20:21.321 --> 20:24.071
AND WHEN SHE FINALLY
GOT CLEAN, GOT HER LIFE

20:24.073 --> 20:28.242
ALL PUT BACK TOGETHER,
KAYSI CAME BACK TO COLORADO.

20:28.244 --> 20:32.580
SHE GOT A GREAT JOB.
SHE WAS HAPPY AGAIN.

20:34.367 --> 20:37.001
AND SHE WAS
COMPLETELY DRUG FREE.

20:37.003 --> 20:41.005
♪♪

20:41.007 --> 20:44.558
BUT ONE DAY, SCOTT SAID THAT
WE HAD A PROBLEM,

20:44.560 --> 20:50.598
THAT HE FOUND A VIAL
AND THAT IT HAD DRUGS IN IT.

20:50.600 --> 20:52.049
I DON'T WANT TO HAVE
TO TELL YOU THIS,

20:52.051 --> 20:55.886
BUT I FOUND THIS
IN THE COUCH.

20:55.888 --> 20:58.489
BUT SHE'S BEEN DOING
SO GOOD.

20:58.491 --> 21:03.160
I WAS SHOCKED WHEN
HE BROUGHT THE VIAL TO ME.

21:03.162 --> 21:06.230
KAYSI SEEMED COMPLETELY CLEAN.

21:06.232 --> 21:08.165
HOW COULD SHE DO IT?

21:08.167 --> 21:09.233
I'M SORRY.

21:09.235 --> 21:12.236
THE BOYS WERE
STILL YOUNG CHILDREN,

21:12.238 --> 21:14.121
AND HE ONLY HAD THEM PART-TIME.

21:14.123 --> 21:16.090
AND I KNEW THAT
I DIDN'T DO DRUGS

21:16.092 --> 21:19.910
AND I KNEW THAT SCOTT
DIDN'T DO DRUGS.

21:19.912 --> 21:22.680
SO, UH, THE ONLY --

21:22.682 --> 21:25.299
THE ONLY NATURAL THING TO THINK

21:25.301 --> 21:28.803
WOULD BE THAT KAYSI
WAS DOING DRUGS AGAIN.

21:30.256 --> 21:32.273
I DON'T WANT TO SEE
MY CHILD KILL HERSELF.

21:32.275 --> 21:34.258
I HAD TO TAKE ACTION.

21:34.260 --> 21:35.393
KAYSI!

21:37.313 --> 21:41.365
I CONFRONTED KAYSI AND TOLD HER
THAT SCOTT HAD FOUND

21:41.367 --> 21:47.488
A VIAL IN THE COUCH, AND I HAD
TO ASSUME IT WAS HERS.

21:47.490 --> 21:51.325
IT'S NOT MINE,
AND IT'S NOT HIS.

21:51.327 --> 21:53.610
KAYSI WAS PLEADING WITH ME.

21:53.612 --> 21:55.880
SHE SAID, "MOM, I SWEAR
THESE ARE NOT MINE.

21:55.882 --> 21:57.614
"I WOULD TELL YOU IF THEY WERE.

21:57.616 --> 21:59.800
THEY ARE NOT MINE."

21:59.802 --> 22:01.886
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME.
I WOULDN'T DO THAT.

22:01.888 --> 22:04.288
I CAN'T TRUST YOU ANYMORE.

22:04.290 --> 22:06.173
[ Voice breaks ]
I DIDN'T BELIEVE MY OWN CHILD.

22:07.593 --> 22:09.793
AND MY PLAN WAS IMMEDIATE.

22:09.795 --> 22:13.130
I WAS GOING TO TAKE HER TO
THE POLICE STATION IMMEDIATELY.

22:13.132 --> 22:17.184
YOU WATCH HER, AND I'M GOING
TO GET MY PURSE FROM UPSTAIRS.

22:17.186 --> 22:18.686
MOM...

22:18.688 --> 22:20.905
I ASKED SCOTT TO STAY WITH KAYSI

22:20.907 --> 22:22.990
WHILE I GRABBED
A COUPLE OF THINGS.

22:22.992 --> 22:25.793
I JUST DIDN'T WANT HER
TO RUN AWAY.

22:25.795 --> 22:34.752
♪♪

22:34.754 --> 22:36.037
HE SAYS, "SHE'S WAITING
IN THE CAR."

22:36.039 --> 22:38.956
AND I SAID, "NO, SHE'S NOT."

22:38.958 --> 22:41.342
AND I GUARANTEE
SHE JUST TOOK OFF.

22:41.344 --> 22:42.993
"NO, SHE'S FINE, SHE'S FINE."

22:42.995 --> 22:47.598
AND SURE ENOUGH,
WHEN WE WENT OUT, SHE WAS GONE.

22:47.600 --> 22:54.021
♪♪

22:54.023 --> 22:56.557
WHEN KAYSI FIRST WENT MISSING,

22:56.559 --> 22:59.643
EVERY SINGLE MOMENT
WAS THINKING,

22:59.645 --> 23:02.113
WHERE COULD SHE POSSIBLY BE?

23:02.115 --> 23:06.233
ALL I KNOW IS KAYSI IS GONE.
SHE WON'T ANSWER MY PHONE CALLS.

23:06.235 --> 23:09.453
WHEN SHE HAD NOT BEEN IN TOUCH
WITH HER BEST FRIEND,

23:09.455 --> 23:10.988
I KNEW THERE WAS A PROBLEM.

23:13.076 --> 23:15.493
I DROVE ALL OVER TOWN
LOOKING FOR HER.

23:15.495 --> 23:17.795
I WOULD THINK I WOULD SEE
SOMEBODY WITH HER HAIR COLOR,

23:17.797 --> 23:19.880
SO I WOULD GO AROUND THE BLOCK

23:19.882 --> 23:22.216
AND COME BACK TO SEE
IF IT WAS HER.

23:22.218 --> 23:24.635
I WOULD SEE PEOPLE IN CARS

23:24.637 --> 23:27.171
THAT LOOKED LIKE
THEY COULD BE HER.

23:27.173 --> 23:29.590
I WENT TO THE POLICE TO FILE
A MISSING PERSONS REPORT,

23:29.592 --> 23:32.209
AND THEY WOULDN'T
LET ME DO THAT,

23:32.211 --> 23:37.598
THAT SHE WAS OVER 18
AND THAT SHE, UM...

23:37.600 --> 23:39.934
IT WAS HER RIGHT TO BE MISSING.

23:39.936 --> 23:41.352
HEY, ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

23:41.354 --> 23:45.656
SCOTT APPEARED
TO BE WORRIED ABOUT ME.

23:45.658 --> 23:47.558
I'M SO FRUSTRATED.

23:47.560 --> 23:50.411
BUT SCOTT WAS TELLING ME
TO CALM DOWN,

23:50.413 --> 23:52.113
JUST LET HER DO HER THING.

23:52.115 --> 23:54.031
SHE'S A GROWN WOMAN.

23:54.033 --> 23:56.400
SHE'LL COME BACK
WHEN SHE'S NOT UPSET WITH YOU.

23:56.402 --> 23:57.535
SHE'S AN ADULT.

23:57.537 --> 23:59.370
SHE'LL COME HOME
WHEN THE TIME IS RIGHT.

24:00.739 --> 24:02.039
MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

24:04.910 --> 24:08.912
I WENT BACK AND FORTH WITH
NEEDING TO BELIEVE HIM,

24:08.914 --> 24:12.183
BECAUSE IF I DIDN'T BELIEVE
WHAT HE WAS TELLING ME,

24:12.185 --> 24:16.670
THEN SOMETHING AWFUL
HAPPENED TO MY DAUGHTER.

24:16.672 --> 24:23.477
♪♪

24:23.479 --> 24:30.468
♪♪

24:30.470 --> 24:34.872
HE SAID, "I'M GOING TO TAKE
A POLYGRAPH TO PROVE YOU WRONG."

24:36.242 --> 24:40.878
HE PASSED EVERY QUESTION
EXCEPT FOR ONE,

24:40.880 --> 24:43.380
AND THAT WAS,
"DO YOU KNOW WHERE KAYSI IS?"

24:43.382 --> 24:44.915
♪♪

24:47.270 --> 24:55.459
♪♪

24:55.461 --> 24:59.346
IS THAT THE CUTEST FACE
YOU'VE EVER SEEN?

24:59.348 --> 25:03.901
YOU CAN SEE THE JOY IN HER FACE.
SHE'S JUST A HAPPY KID.

25:03.903 --> 25:07.805
[ CRYING ] KAYSI WAS STILL
VERY TRUSTING AT THAT AGE.

25:07.807 --> 25:09.640
SHE HAD NOTHING IN HER LIFE

25:09.642 --> 25:13.077
THAT WOULD TELL HER
SHE SHOULDN'T TRUST PEOPLE.

25:13.079 --> 25:16.463
IT'S...

25:16.465 --> 25:18.299
IT'S JUST SO SOON AFTER THIS

25:18.301 --> 25:21.268
THAT EVERYTHING WENT SO BAD.

25:21.270 --> 25:22.653
YOU JUST...

25:25.041 --> 25:26.874
I-I WOULD LIKE TO CRAWL
THROUGH THE PICTURE

25:26.876 --> 25:28.792
AND PREVENT EVERYTHING.

25:28.794 --> 25:34.748
♪♪

25:34.750 --> 25:40.721
♪♪

25:40.723 --> 25:43.123
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

25:43.125 --> 25:47.628
KAYSI AND C.B. HAD BEEN DATING
MAYBE FOUR OR FIVE MONTHS.

25:47.630 --> 25:50.481
-HELLO?
-Lori, it's C.B.

25:50.483 --> 25:53.317
A FEW DAYS AFTER
KAYSI LEFT THE HOUSE,

25:53.319 --> 25:54.635
C.B. CALLED ME

25:54.637 --> 25:57.571
AND SAID THAT THEY HAD BEEN
STAYING AT A MOTEL,

25:57.573 --> 26:00.641
THAT SCOTT HAD PROVIDED
THE MONEY FOR THE MOTEL,

26:00.643 --> 26:03.577
AND THAT HE HAD BEEN
TAKING KAYSI TO WORK.

26:03.579 --> 26:05.479
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

26:05.481 --> 26:09.149
I DIDN'T BELIEVE
WHAT HE WAS TELLING ME,

26:09.151 --> 26:14.455
BUT C.B. INSISTED THAT
WHEN KAYSI FIRST WENT MISSING,

26:14.457 --> 26:17.007
SCOTT GAVE HER MONEY,
PUT HER ON HER BIKE,

26:17.009 --> 26:19.043
AND TOLD HER TO TAKE OFF.

26:19.045 --> 26:21.178
HE WOULDN'T HIDE THAT
FROM ME, C.B.

26:21.180 --> 26:23.180
HE PUT HER UP IN A MOTEL.

26:23.182 --> 26:27.134
HE HAD BEEN PICKING HER UP EVERY
DAY AND TAKING HER TO WORK.

26:27.136 --> 26:29.186
AND THE LAST DAY
HE PICKED HER UP

26:29.188 --> 26:33.007
AND TOOK HER TO WORK,
SHE NEVER CAME HOME.

26:33.009 --> 26:35.225
NO, THAT'S NOT RIGHT.

26:35.227 --> 26:37.978
SCOTT WOULD TELL ME THIS.

26:37.980 --> 26:41.115
AND C.B. SAID, "I DON'T KNOW
WHY HE'S LYING TO YOU.

26:41.117 --> 26:43.850
"I SAW THE TRUCK.
I SAW HIM PICK HER UP."

26:43.852 --> 26:46.236
HE WAS AFRAID
SOMETHING HAPPENED.

26:46.238 --> 26:52.543
♪♪

26:52.545 --> 26:58.299
♪♪

26:58.301 --> 27:02.269
I FELT SOMETHING WAS
DEFINITELY AMISS.

27:02.271 --> 27:05.873
BUT SCOTT TOLD ME HE WAS
USING HIS RESOURCES

27:05.875 --> 27:08.676
WITH THE FBI TO ASK AROUND
AND ASK ABOUT HER,

27:08.678 --> 27:10.043
AND NOBODY HAD SEEN HER.

27:10.045 --> 27:12.012
♪♪

27:12.014 --> 27:13.764
[ LOCKS CLICK ]

27:13.766 --> 27:14.815
SCOTT?

27:14.817 --> 27:15.849
WHEN SCOTT CAME BACK,

27:15.851 --> 27:18.652
I ASKED HIM WHEN
HE LAST PICKED HER UP.

27:18.654 --> 27:21.572
-WHAT'S UP?
-C.B. CALLED.

27:21.574 --> 27:22.823
AND?

27:22.825 --> 27:24.408
AND HE SAID THAT YOU'VE BEEN

27:24.410 --> 27:26.777
TAKING KAYSI TO WORK
ALL THIS TIME.

27:26.779 --> 27:27.995
WHAT?

27:27.997 --> 27:30.280
AND SCOTT SAID
THAT C.B. IS LYING.

27:30.282 --> 27:33.534
HE DID NOT PICK HER UP
AND TAKE HER TO WORK THAT DAY.

27:33.536 --> 27:34.618
THAT'S WHAT HE SAID,

27:34.620 --> 27:37.237
THAT YOU PICKED HER UP
FROM THE MOTEL.

27:37.239 --> 27:39.456
C.B.'s A DRUG ADDICT.

27:39.458 --> 27:40.924
HE LIES.

27:40.926 --> 27:46.413
SCOTT KEPT CONVINCING ME THAT
C.B. WAS ON DRUGS.

27:46.415 --> 27:47.798
WHO SHOULD I BELIEVE,

27:47.800 --> 27:50.634
A NORMAL-THINKING PERSON
OR A DRUG ADDICT?

27:50.636 --> 27:52.519
I WAS JUST EXTREMELY CONFUSED.

27:52.521 --> 27:55.255
JUST TELL ME IF YOU'VE
SEEN HER OR NOT.

27:55.257 --> 27:57.224
THIS IS CRAZY.

27:57.226 --> 27:58.892
HOW CAN YOU SAY THAT?

27:58.894 --> 28:02.062
I'M HELPING YOU,
AND YOU THINK I'VE SEEN HER?

28:02.064 --> 28:04.398
HE KIND OF
THREW IT BACK ON ME,

28:04.400 --> 28:06.400
LIKE, "HOW COULD YOU DOUBT ME?"

28:06.402 --> 28:08.318
BUT HE SAID,
"IF I PASS A POLYGRAPH,

28:08.320 --> 28:11.155
"CAN WE JUST NOT
TALK ABOUT IT AGAIN?"

28:11.157 --> 28:13.240
WOULD THAT CONVINCE YOU?

28:15.444 --> 28:19.546
ACTUALLY, YES. IT WOULD.

28:21.950 --> 28:23.950
I THINK HE THOUGHT I WOULD SAY,

28:23.952 --> 28:27.454
"NO, LET'S NOT WASTE THE MONEY.
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

28:27.456 --> 28:28.955
"YOU'RE WILLING
TO TAKE A POLYGRAPH,

28:28.957 --> 28:31.308
SO OBVIOUSLY YOU'RE INNOCENT."

28:31.310 --> 28:32.426
ALL RIGHT, IF IT'LL GET YOU

28:32.428 --> 28:36.013
TO TRUST ME AGAIN,
I'LL SET SOMETHING UP.

28:36.015 --> 28:37.765
OKAY.

28:37.767 --> 28:40.017
♪♪

28:40.019 --> 28:42.102
I WENT AHEAD AND LET HIM
GO FORWARD WITH IT.

28:42.104 --> 28:46.990
♪♪

28:46.992 --> 28:50.143
WE WENT TO THE CENTER
TO DO THE POLYGRAPH.

28:50.145 --> 28:52.546
I WAITED IN THE WAITING ROOM.

28:52.548 --> 28:56.316
HE WENT IN TO GET HIS TEST.

28:56.318 --> 28:59.002
AND WHEN THEY OPENED
THE DOOR AND CAME OUT...

28:59.004 --> 29:01.038
-HELLO.
-HELLO.

29:01.040 --> 29:05.492
...HE SAID HE'D PASSED
EVERY QUESTION EXCEPT FOR ONE,

29:05.494 --> 29:08.045
AND THAT WAS,
"DO YOU KNOW WHERE KAYSI IS?"

29:08.047 --> 29:10.214
♪♪

29:10.216 --> 29:13.517
BESIDES THAT, EVERYTHING SEEMS
TO CHECK OUT.

29:13.519 --> 29:17.104
SCOTT QUICKLY EXPLAINED TO ME
THAT BECAUSE HE WAS PROBABLY

29:17.106 --> 29:19.223
ONE OF THE LAST OF US
TO SEE HER,

29:19.225 --> 29:23.310
THAT'S WHERE HE THOUGHT THAT
THAT DOUBT CAME IN.

29:23.312 --> 29:24.812
LIKE, "YES, I KNOW
WHERE SHE LAST WAS,

29:24.814 --> 29:26.563
AND THAT WAS IN FRONT
OF THE HOUSE."

29:26.565 --> 29:30.984
AND THAT SEEMED LIKE
A REASONABLE ANSWER TO ME.

29:30.986 --> 29:34.538
I FELT RELIEVED
THAT HE PASSED HIS TEST.

29:34.540 --> 29:38.325
I CAN SET ASIDE
DOUBTING HIM AT ALL

29:38.327 --> 29:40.410
AND DO THINGS THAT ARE
MORE PRODUCTIVE.

29:40.412 --> 29:41.578
SCOTT, I'M SO SORRY.

29:41.580 --> 29:44.748
I'M JUST SO WORRIED
ABOUT KAYSI.

29:44.750 --> 29:46.250
YOU CAN TRUST ME, RIGHT?

29:46.252 --> 29:47.634
YES.

29:47.636 --> 29:54.341
♪♪

29:54.343 --> 30:01.081
♪♪

30:01.083 --> 30:04.151
ONE DAY, SCOTT TOLD ME THAT
HE WENT INTO KAYSI'S BEDROOM

30:04.153 --> 30:06.520
AND HE FOUND
HER MAKEUP CASE GONE.

30:06.522 --> 30:09.823
♪♪

30:09.825 --> 30:11.825
SEE, IT'S MISSING.

30:11.827 --> 30:15.996
SO THAT IS PROOF
THAT SHE WAS AT THE HOUSE,

30:15.998 --> 30:18.115
THAT SHE IS JUST AVOIDING ME.

30:19.752 --> 30:22.085
AND HE SAYS, "LOOK,
THIS IS KAYSI'S NECKLACE.

30:22.087 --> 30:24.371
"IT'S HANGING ON HER DOORKNOB.

30:24.373 --> 30:27.090
"THIS IS THE NECKLACE
THAT C.B. GAVE HER.

30:27.092 --> 30:28.876
"I THINK THAT'S
A PRETTY CLEAR MESSAGE

30:28.878 --> 30:30.744
"THAT SHE WANTS IT
GIVEN BACK TO C.B.

30:30.746 --> 30:33.213
"AND THAT SHE'S NOT
WITH C.B. ANYMORE."

30:34.917 --> 30:37.250
AND HE SAYS THAT
I NEED TO STOP WORRYING

30:37.252 --> 30:39.603
AND THAT SHE'LL COME BACK
AROUND WHEN SHE'S READY.

30:39.605 --> 30:41.104
SHE DOESN'T WANT YOU
TO CALL THE COPS ON HER.

30:41.106 --> 30:42.890
THAT'S THE ONLY REASON
SHE'S NOT HERE.

30:45.144 --> 30:48.145
IT MADE ME FEEL GOOD
THAT SHE WAS AROUND.

30:48.147 --> 30:50.864
♪♪

30:50.866 --> 30:52.265
THOSE MOMENTS ARE GIVING ME HOPE

30:52.267 --> 30:55.986
THAT SHE WAS, IN FACT,
AT THE HOUSE.

30:55.988 --> 30:58.121
I WENT INTO HER ROOM OFTEN.

30:59.375 --> 31:01.575
I WOULD LEAVE MONEY ON THE BED,

31:01.577 --> 31:03.660
JUST IN CASE
SHE WOULD COME BACK.

31:05.998 --> 31:08.916
SHE NEVER TOOK MONEY,

31:08.918 --> 31:12.336
BUT I WAS STILL HOLDING OUT HOPE
THAT SHE WAS ALIVE SOMEWHERE.

31:12.338 --> 31:21.762
♪♪

31:21.764 --> 31:25.566
ONE NIGHT, SCOTT JUST DIDN'T
COME HOME,

31:25.568 --> 31:28.018
AND A DETECTIVE KNOCKED
ON MY DOOR.

31:28.020 --> 31:31.104
AND AT THIS POINT, KAYSI HAD
BEEN MISSING WELL OVER A YEAR.

31:31.106 --> 31:32.606
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

31:34.309 --> 31:37.361
AND HE SAID, "I NEED TO TALK
TO SCOTT KIMBALL."

31:37.363 --> 31:38.779
AND I SAID, "HE'S NOT HERE."

31:38.781 --> 31:41.147
SCOTT'S OUT WORKING ON
A CASE FOR YOU GUYS RIGHT NOW.

31:41.149 --> 31:43.417
I'M SURE YOUR OFFICE
CAN TRACK HIM DOWN.

31:43.419 --> 31:45.919
THE DETECTIVE SAID THAT
THAT WAS A LIE.

31:45.921 --> 31:50.507
HE DOESN'T WORK FOR US.
WE'RE INVESTIGATING HIM.

31:50.509 --> 31:54.661
HE WAS NOT AN AGENT.
HE WAS AN INFORMANT.

31:54.663 --> 31:57.564
♪♪

31:59.301 --> 32:03.904
♪♪

32:03.906 --> 32:06.273
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

32:06.275 --> 32:08.358
McLeod: A DETECTIVE KNOCKED
ON MY DOOR

32:08.360 --> 32:11.612
AND HE SAID, "I NEED TO TALK
TO SCOTT KIMBALL."

32:11.614 --> 32:13.980
SCOTT'S OUT WORKING ON
A CASE FOR YOU GUYS RIGHT NOW.

32:13.982 --> 32:16.833
HE DOESN'T WORK FOR US.
WE'RE INVESTIGATING HIM.

32:18.420 --> 32:19.536
WHAT?

32:19.538 --> 32:21.588
I FOUND OUT
PRETTY MUCH EVERYTHING

32:21.590 --> 32:23.823
HE HAD EVERY SAID TO ME
WAS A LIE,

32:23.825 --> 32:27.661
INCLUDING HIS EMPLOYMENT STATUS
WITH THE FBI.

32:27.663 --> 32:29.730
HE WAS NOT AN AGENT.

32:29.732 --> 32:33.467
NO, THAT'S NOT RIGHT.
SCOTT WORKS FOR THE FBI.

32:33.469 --> 32:34.668
NO, HE DOESN'T.

32:34.670 --> 32:39.906
HE IS AN FBI INFORMANT,
BUT HE'S A CONVICTED FELON.

32:39.908 --> 32:43.243
HE HAD WRITTEN
A BAD CHECK IN MONTANA

32:43.245 --> 32:45.045
AND HAD SERVED TIME
FOR THAT.

32:45.981 --> 32:48.548
AND NOW HE WAS AN INFORMANT.

32:48.550 --> 32:53.570
HE WAS A BAD GUY
CATCHING WORSE GUYS.

32:53.572 --> 32:57.741
BUT THERE'S A PROBLEM --
HE WAS ON THE RUN.

32:57.743 --> 33:00.327
BEYOND HIS STATUS AS
AN INFORMANT,

33:00.329 --> 33:03.330
SCOTT IS LINKED TO BEING
THE LAST ONE

33:03.332 --> 33:06.866
TO SEE
CERTAIN MISSING PERSONS.

33:06.868 --> 33:08.135
COULD I SHOW YOU
SOME PICTURES?

33:08.137 --> 33:09.169
MM-HMM.

33:09.171 --> 33:10.470
DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THIS WOMAN?

33:10.472 --> 33:13.340
♪♪

33:13.342 --> 33:14.841
McLeod: JENNIFER MARCUM
WAS MISSING.

33:16.345 --> 33:19.596
I SAID I THINK THAT'S THE GIRL
HE TOLD ME WAS, IN FACT, DEAD.

33:19.598 --> 33:24.351
HE WAS ON HER CASE,
TRYING TO SOLVE HER MURDER.

33:24.353 --> 33:25.852
AND HOW ABOUT THIS WOMAN?

33:27.856 --> 33:30.557
THEY KNEW LeANN EMRY
WAS MISSING.

33:30.559 --> 33:33.360
SCOTT NEVER MENTIONED LeANN.

33:33.362 --> 33:36.079
I NEVER KNEW ANYTHING ABOUT HER.

33:36.081 --> 33:40.333
THE DETECTIVE ASKED IF I KNEW
IF THERE WERE

33:40.335 --> 33:43.503
ANY OTHER MISSING PEOPLE
SURROUNDING SCOTT.

33:43.505 --> 33:46.923
AND I SAID MY DAUGHTER
IS STILL MISSING.

33:46.925 --> 33:48.675
MY DAUGHTER KAYSI.

33:48.677 --> 33:50.410
♪♪

33:50.412 --> 33:52.262
Y-YOU DAUGHTER?

33:52.264 --> 33:53.680
AND IT WAS VERY OBVIOUS

33:53.682 --> 33:57.584
THAT HE HAD NO IDEA
THAT KAYSI WAS EVER MISSING.

33:57.586 --> 33:59.720
ALL RIGHT, I-I THINK
THAT I SHOULD

33:59.722 --> 34:02.305
TAKE YOU DOWN TO THE STATION.
-YES, YES.

34:02.307 --> 34:05.058
AND HE SAID, "I THINK WE'RE
IN TROUBLE HERE."

34:05.060 --> 34:14.818
♪♪

34:19.441 --> 34:22.876
SCOTT STARTED CALLING ME
AND TELLING ME

34:22.878 --> 34:24.828
THAT THEY HAVE THE WRONG GUY,

34:24.830 --> 34:26.630
DON'T LISTEN TO WHAT
THEY'RE SAYING,

34:26.632 --> 34:28.548
THEY'RE JUST TRYING
TO FRAME HIM.

34:36.892 --> 34:38.391
IT WAS EASIER FOR ME TO BELIEVE

34:38.393 --> 34:41.144
THAT THEY MIGHT BE LYING TO ME
AND SETTING HIM UP

34:41.146 --> 34:43.013
THAN TO BELIEVE THAT
SHE WAS GONE.

34:46.685 --> 34:47.934
YOU HAVE TO KEEP IN MIND,

34:47.936 --> 34:51.188
I'M STILL HOLDING OUT HOPE
THAT KAYSI IS OKAY.

34:51.190 --> 34:56.326
IF I STOP BELIEVING WHAT HE'S
TELLING ME, THEN IT'S REAL.

34:56.328 --> 34:58.978
SHE COULD REALLY BE GONE.

34:58.980 --> 35:01.581
I WOULD PREFER TO THINK
I'M LOSING MY MIND

35:01.583 --> 35:04.084
THAN TO ACCEPT THE FACT THAT
SHE'S REALLY GONE.

35:04.086 --> 35:05.819
I WANTED HIM TO CONVINCE ME

35:05.821 --> 35:08.205
THAT HE WAS TELLING ME
THE TRUTH.

35:08.207 --> 35:17.397
♪♪

35:17.399 --> 35:19.850
THE FBI CALLED ME AND THEY SAID

35:19.852 --> 35:26.773
THAT KAYSI'S DAD AND I NEEDED
TO COME DOWN TO TALK TO THEM.

35:26.775 --> 35:30.777
AND WE WENT IN
AND WE SAT DOWN,

35:30.779 --> 35:33.196
AND THEY STARTED TALKING.

35:33.198 --> 35:38.618
AND I'M JUST WATCHING THEM AND
HOPING THAT THEY SAY IT FAST,

35:38.620 --> 35:40.854
JUST RIP OFF THE BAND-AID FAST.

35:40.856 --> 35:44.374
THE OTHER PART OF ME IS SAYING,
"I DON'T WANNA HEAR IT."

35:44.376 --> 35:47.026
NOW, THIS ISN'T FINAL
NOR DOES IT MEAN

35:47.028 --> 35:50.163
THAT IT'S YOUR DAUGHTER,
BUT WE HAVE FOUND A BODY.

35:50.165 --> 35:51.998
OH, NO.

35:52.000 --> 35:53.466
KAYSI!

35:53.468 --> 35:59.639
WE WERE TOLD THAT HUNTERS
HAD FOUND...

35:59.641 --> 36:01.258
HUMAN REMAINS.

36:01.260 --> 36:04.210
THEY WEREN'T SURE WHO IT WAS.

36:04.212 --> 36:07.397
WE'RE GONNA NEED SOME DNA TO
IDENTIFY THE REMAINS.

36:07.399 --> 36:09.516
WE'D LIKE TO TAKE
SOME SAMPLES.

36:09.518 --> 36:12.152
I HAD KAYSI'S BABY TEETH,

36:12.154 --> 36:16.740
AND SO THEY USED --
THEY USED THEM

36:16.742 --> 36:19.075
TO IDENTIFY HER.

36:19.077 --> 36:25.415
♪♪

36:25.417 --> 36:27.868
I'M SORRY, GUYS.
[ SNIFFLES ]

36:27.870 --> 36:30.337
[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

36:30.339 --> 36:35.909
<i> ♪♪</i>

36:35.911 --> 36:38.128
<i> [ BABY KAYSI GIGGLING ]</i>

36:38.130 --> 36:41.715
KAYSI WAS PROBABLY
ONLY ABOUT 6 MONTHS THEN.

36:41.717 --> 36:43.717
SHE WAS NOT READY TO WALK,

36:43.719 --> 36:47.086
BUT SHE STILL THOUGHT
IT WAS FUN TO TRY.

36:47.088 --> 36:49.139
HER LITTLE LEGS
WERE LIKE JELL-O.

36:49.141 --> 36:51.591
SHE WAS JUST
A LITTLE GIGGLE BUCKET.

36:51.593 --> 36:55.695
THAT WAS KAYSI'S PERSONALITY
FROM THE VERY BEGINNING.

36:55.697 --> 36:59.098
HAPPY, NOTHING UPSET HER.

36:59.100 --> 37:03.119
SHE DESERVED A LOT MORE
IN LIFE THAN SHE GOT.

37:03.121 --> 37:05.271
I JUST...I-I MISS HER.

37:05.273 --> 37:08.625
I-I MISS HER ENERGY.

37:10.212 --> 37:16.333
IF WE ALL JUST HAD
A-A RESET BUTTON, JUST ONE,

37:16.335 --> 37:20.720
I-I WOULD DEFINITELY CHOOSE
TO GO BACK TO THIS TIME.

37:22.224 --> 37:24.958
THERE ARE DAYS I THINK I HAVE
FORGIVEN MYSELF,

37:24.960 --> 37:29.295
BUT IF I TAKE TOO MUCH TIME
TO THINK ABOUT IT,

37:29.297 --> 37:33.132
I'M THE ONE WHO BROUGHT HIM
INTO OUR LIVES.

37:33.134 --> 37:35.134
THERE'S NOBODY ELSE
AND NOTHING ELSE

37:35.136 --> 37:39.305
THAT'S RESPONSIBLE FOR...
HER BEING GONE.

37:39.307 --> 37:45.645
♪♪

37:45.647 --> 37:51.952
♪♪

37:51.954 --> 37:54.254
THEY WERE
INVESTIGATING THE HOUSE

37:54.256 --> 37:55.455
AND LOOKING THROUGH EVERYTHING,

37:55.457 --> 37:57.340
AND THEY HAD
PULLED BACK THE CARPET

37:57.342 --> 38:00.760
AND THEY FOUND BLOOD
THAT BELONGED TO UNCLE TERRY.

38:00.762 --> 38:03.663
UNCLE TERRY HAD BEEN KILLED
IN MY LIVING ROOM.

38:03.665 --> 38:10.303
I FLASHED BACK TO THE COUCH
BEING OUT BY THE POOL

38:10.305 --> 38:12.389
AND, UM, NEVER SEEING
UNCLE TERRY AGAIN.

38:28.657 --> 38:30.206
YOU MEAN YOU<i> WON'T</i> DO IT.

38:30.208 --> 38:37.464
♪♪

38:37.466 --> 38:39.916
WE ALL KNOW THAT
ALL OF THOSE PEOPLE

38:39.918 --> 38:42.218
DIED AT THE HAND
OF SCOTT KIMBALL.

38:42.220 --> 38:47.540
♪♪

38:47.542 --> 38:50.427
THIS IS LeANN EMRY.

38:50.429 --> 38:52.979
I BELIEVE SHE WAS

38:52.981 --> 38:55.715
THE FIRST VICTIM OF SCOTT.

38:55.717 --> 38:58.902
LeANN'S BOYFRIEND
WAS IN PRISON WITH SCOTT.

38:58.904 --> 39:02.455
THAT'S HOW HE MEETS VICTIMS,
THROUGH THE BOYFRIENDS.

39:03.492 --> 39:05.224
THIS IS JENNIFER MARCUM.

39:05.226 --> 39:10.130
THE JENNIFER HE WAS TALKING
ABOUT BEING MURDERED

39:10.132 --> 39:13.466
AND THE JENNIFER WHO HAD
THE TOWNHOUSE

39:13.468 --> 39:16.036
THAT HE WAS LIVING IN,
AFTER HE HAD KILLED HER,

39:16.038 --> 39:18.004
IT WAS, IN FACT,
THE SAME JENNIFER.

39:18.006 --> 39:20.457
♪♪

39:20.459 --> 39:24.844
UNKNOWINGLY,
I LIVED IN HER HOME,

39:24.846 --> 39:26.763
I SLEPT IN HER BED,

39:26.765 --> 39:31.468
I SAT ON HER SOFA,
I ATE OFF OF HER DISHES.

39:31.470 --> 39:33.103
IT MADE ME SICK TO MY STOMACH.

39:33.105 --> 39:42.062
♪♪

39:42.064 --> 39:46.466
SCOTT PLEAD GUILTY TO TWO
COUNTS OF SECOND DEGREE MURDER

39:46.468 --> 39:48.435
IN EXCHANGE
FOR A REDUCED SENTENCE

39:48.437 --> 39:53.940
AND TO GIVE THE LOCATION
OF ALL OF THE MISSING PEOPLE.

39:53.942 --> 39:55.158
THE SCARY PART IS,

39:55.160 --> 39:58.244
IS HE WILL GET PAROLE
IF HE IS UP FOR PAROLE.

39:58.246 --> 40:01.381
HE IS EXTREMELY CONVINCING.

40:01.383 --> 40:03.116
WE NEED TO KEEP HIM BEHIND BARS,

40:03.118 --> 40:06.820
HE IS DANGEROUS TO ANYBODY
HE COMES IN CONTACT WITH.

40:06.822 --> 40:07.954
BUT MORE THAN LIKELY,

40:07.956 --> 40:09.756
I WON'T BE HERE
FOR THE PAROLE HEARINGS.

40:09.758 --> 40:15.678
♪♪

40:15.680 --> 40:21.184
♪♪

40:21.186 --> 40:24.137
THEY GAVE ME SIX MONTHS
TO TWO YEARS.

40:24.139 --> 40:29.075
AFTER THE SHOCK WORE OFF,
I WAS ACTUALLY KIND OF EXCITED

40:29.077 --> 40:31.995
THAT I GET TO LEAVE SOONER
AND GET TO BE WITH MY KIDDO.

40:33.215 --> 40:39.085
WHEN I PASS,
MY PLAN IS TO BE CREMATED,

40:39.087 --> 40:42.421
AND THEY WILL OPEN
KAYSI'S CASKET,

40:42.423 --> 40:46.526
AND MY CREMAINS WILL BE
IN KAYSI'S CASKET.

40:46.528 --> 40:48.427
♪♪

40:48.429 --> 40:51.948
WE'LL BE TOGETHER IN HEAVEN.

40:51.950 --> 40:55.702
THAT'S THE ONLY THING
THAT GETS ME THROUGH.

40:55.704 --> 40:57.537
THERE'S SOMETHING BETTER
WAITING.

40:59.124 --> 41:01.407
KAYSI IS THE LIGHT
AT THE END OF THE TUNNEL.

41:01.409 --> 41:03.776
KAYSI IS WHERE I'M HEADED.

41:04.946 --> 41:06.746
THERE IS WHO I PICTURE I HEAVEN.

41:06.748 --> 41:12.418
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
I WILL LOOK LIKE, EXACTLY,

41:12.420 --> 41:15.388
BUT THIS IS THE PERSON
THAT I PICTURE.

41:15.390 --> 41:19.092
AND SHE'LL BE
THE RIGHT HEIGHT TO HUG AND...

41:19.094 --> 41:23.429
♪♪

41:23.431 --> 41:25.298
SHE -- SHE'S...

41:25.300 --> 41:27.150
SHE'S JUST WAITING FOR ME, TOO.

41:27.152 --> 41:31.271
♪♪
